7. SHAREHOLDING STRUCTURE
7.1 The Parties acknowledge that the shareholding structure of the Business School, established in Hawke's Bay as of January 8, 1994, shall be as follows:
(a) The Investor shall hold 60% of the total issued shares;
(b) The Management Team shall collectively hold 20% of the total issued shares;
(c) The Public Health and Welfare Trust shall hold 10% of the total issued shares;
(d) The remaining 10% shall be reserved for future allocation to key employees and/or partners, subject to the approval of the Investor and the Management Team.
7.2 Any changes to the shareholding structure shall be made in accordance with the provisions of this Agreement and applicable laws and regulations.
